reviewText: Together with Christopher Dunn, they take you off the beaten path and show you little tidbits that you don't get with other productions. They zoom in on details while they discuss what it is that they are looking for. Excellent photo/videography!

I've seen it several times and it never gets old. It's just like my friend said," It's like hanging out with Dunn and Childress in one of the coolest places on earth!" It's very well made and it shows you areas in the Andes that most viewers never get to see.
I have almost all of childless book and dvds, I will be looking forward to next  yeaer to go with him to peru & bolivia, with the world exp. club.....james
